1
00:00:22,190 --> 00:00:23,050
Have you got it?

2
00:00:23,600 --> 00:00:24,200
Of course.

3
00:00:24,250 --> 00:00:26,190
I'm the Reception Envoy
appointed by my father.

4
00:00:26,190 --> 00:00:27,640
They would naturally give me the pass.

5
00:00:27,640 --> 00:00:28,230
Good.

6
00:00:28,480 --> 00:00:29,830
Then let's depart immediately.

7
00:00:29,830 --> 00:00:32,159
Go 30 li east
and then switch to waterways.

8
00:00:32,320 --> 00:00:34,590
We should be able to reach
Qingluan Pass within 5 days.

9
00:00:34,590 --> 00:00:35,710
Once at Qingluan Pass,

10
00:00:35,710 --> 00:00:36,670
take Xiao Ran and the others

11
00:00:36,670 --> 00:00:38,400
and continue east to Lincheng.

12
00:00:38,640 --> 00:00:40,430
The rest of the envoy team turns south

13
00:00:40,430 --> 00:00:41,600
and heads to Qiongzhou.

14
00:00:41,600 --> 00:00:44,390
Guide Envoy Lord Zhan Ziyu has arrived.

15
00:00:49,530 --> 00:00:50,330
Leave it to me.

16
00:01:02,000 --> 00:01:03,240
Your Highness.

17
00:01:03,750 --> 00:01:07,200
Her Majesty heard that you're going
to Qiongzhou with King Ximeng.

18
00:01:07,200 --> 00:01:10,150
You hurriedly got the imperial pass
from the Ministry of Rites yesterday.

19
00:01:10,150 --> 00:01:11,870
I didn't expect you to leave today.

20
00:01:11,870 --> 00:01:15,070
I wonder why you're in such a hurry.

21
00:01:15,430 --> 00:01:17,560
What are you talking about, Lord Zhan?

22
00:01:17,560 --> 00:01:19,280
My royal parents gave me the grace

23
00:01:19,280 --> 00:01:20,789
to be the Reception Envoy

24
00:01:21,039 --> 00:01:23,039
and accompany King Ximeng on a tour.

25
00:01:23,070 --> 00:01:24,560
How dare I slack off?

26
00:01:24,840 --> 00:01:27,170
Your Highness, you're absolutely right.

27
00:01:27,480 --> 00:01:29,680
But I find it very strange.

28
00:01:31,200 --> 00:01:32,660
Qiongzhou is a long way off

29
00:01:32,750 --> 00:01:34,759
and has no scenery.

30
00:01:34,950 --> 00:01:36,590
King Ximeng came from afar,

31
00:01:38,680 --> 00:01:41,920
so he should enjoy
the beautiful scenery of Biantang.

32
00:01:42,070 --> 00:01:44,560
Why go all the way to Qiongzhou?

33
00:01:44,950 --> 00:01:45,840
Could it be...

34
00:01:47,479 --> 00:01:50,310
that there is something special
about Qiongzhou?

35
00:01:52,150 --> 00:01:53,640
Don't ask, Lord Zhan.

36
00:01:54,780 --> 00:01:56,580
I'm wondering too.

37
00:01:56,920 --> 00:01:58,759
This old man from Ximeng is very weird.

38
00:01:58,759 --> 00:02:01,070
He insists on going
to that damn Qiongzhou.

39
00:02:01,070 --> 00:02:02,280
I'm very reluctant.

40
00:02:02,280 --> 00:02:04,210
How did I end up with such a hard job?

41
00:02:05,840 --> 00:02:07,900
Why speak such words, Your Highness?

42
00:02:08,289 --> 00:02:10,320
Her Majesty has always loved you the most.

43
00:02:10,320 --> 00:02:12,320
To show sympathy for your hard work,

44
00:02:12,320 --> 00:02:14,640
she specially sent me as a Guide Envoy

45
00:02:15,240 --> 00:02:16,100
to clear the way

46
00:02:16,750 --> 00:02:18,800
for you and King Ximeng.

47
00:02:19,470 --> 00:02:20,840
That's not necessary.

48
00:02:20,840 --> 00:02:22,120
Going to Qiongzhou is a trivial matter.

49
00:02:22,120 --> 00:02:23,520
How can I bother you, Lord Zhan?

50
00:02:23,520 --> 00:02:25,180
You are wrong, Your Highness.

51
00:02:26,400 --> 00:02:29,150
Receiving foreigners
is an important matter for the country.

52
00:02:29,150 --> 00:02:31,430
How can you say it's a trivial matter?

53
00:02:31,590 --> 00:02:32,520
What's more,

54
00:02:33,800 --> 00:02:35,870
this is Her Majesty's decree.

55
00:02:36,680 --> 00:02:38,150
Let alone me,

56
00:02:39,260 --> 00:02:40,350
even you

57
00:02:40,430 --> 00:02:42,630
should follow it carefully.

58
00:02:50,150 --> 00:02:51,150
Your Highness.

59
00:02:51,710 --> 00:02:54,280
Since Lord Zhan has conveyed
Her Majesty's gracious intention,

60
00:02:54,280 --> 00:02:56,200
I can't naturally disappoint him.

61
00:02:56,200 --> 00:02:57,560
Let's travel

62
00:02:57,560 --> 00:02:58,680
with Lord Zhan.

63
00:04:23,770 --> 00:04:29,310
[REBIRTH]

64
00:04:29,850 --> 00:04:32,180
[Episode 14]

65
00:04:48,490 --> 00:04:52,440
[Qingluan Pass]

66
00:04:56,920 --> 00:04:57,720
Your Highness,

67
00:04:57,720 --> 00:04:59,390
we have arrived at Qingluan Pass.

68
00:04:59,390 --> 00:05:00,560
There are 2 forks ahead.

69
00:05:00,560 --> 00:05:01,950
One to the east and one to the west.

70
00:05:01,950 --> 00:05:03,870
Both can reach Qiongzhou Prefecture.

71
00:05:03,870 --> 00:05:05,510
Go east. Set off immediately.

72
00:05:05,510 --> 00:05:06,800
Wait, Your Highness.

73
00:05:07,480 --> 00:05:09,210
To go to Qiongzhou Prefecture,

74
00:05:09,240 --> 00:05:10,720
you should head west.

75
00:05:11,310 --> 00:05:12,870
The terrain in the east is steep,

76
00:05:12,870 --> 00:05:14,430
with many mountains and wild beasts.

77
00:05:14,430 --> 00:05:16,030
The west is an official road.

78
00:05:16,120 --> 00:05:17,480
There are post stations along the way,

79
00:05:17,480 --> 00:05:19,210
which is much more convenient.

80
00:05:19,720 --> 00:05:21,650
The road in the east is a bit rugged,

81
00:05:21,720 --> 00:05:23,060
but there are shortcuts.

82
00:05:23,060 --> 00:05:25,720
We can arrive
at Qiongzhou Prefecture earlier.

83
00:05:25,830 --> 00:05:26,950
That's strange.

84
00:05:27,360 --> 00:05:29,000
You don't take the flat official road

85
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:30,190
in the west,

86
00:05:30,270 --> 00:05:31,600
but insists on going
to the deserted, dangerous mountains

87
00:05:31,600 --> 00:05:33,000
in the east.

88
00:05:33,240 --> 00:05:34,390
Could it be that the east

89
00:05:34,390 --> 00:05:36,190
has something special?

90
00:05:36,870 --> 00:05:37,480
Or is it that King Ximeng

91
00:05:37,480 --> 00:05:40,000
and you have ulterior motives?

92
00:05:40,630 --> 00:05:41,390
You are not

93
00:05:41,720 --> 00:05:43,190
going to Qiongzhou at all,

94
00:05:43,920 --> 00:05:45,640
but somewhere else, are you?

95
00:05:47,680 --> 00:05:49,600
Lord Zhan, you're indeed smart.

96
00:05:50,000 --> 00:05:50,870
You can tell at a glance

97
00:05:50,870 --> 00:05:52,530
that I have ulterior motives.

98
00:05:52,680 --> 00:05:54,040
To tell you the truth, Lord Zhan,

99
00:05:54,040 --> 00:05:57,060
it's said that heading east
from here will pass by Yingchuan.

100
00:05:57,060 --> 00:05:58,800
There is not only good wine and food

101
00:05:58,800 --> 00:06:00,460
but also countless beauties.

102
00:06:01,240 --> 00:06:02,860
I do have some selfish motives

103
00:06:02,860 --> 00:06:04,320
and want to experience it.

104
00:06:04,430 --> 00:06:06,160
But since you're the Guide Envoy,

105
00:06:06,160 --> 00:06:07,830
I will listen to you.

106
00:06:08,270 --> 00:06:09,470
By Lord Zhan's order,

107
00:06:09,510 --> 00:06:11,440
take the official road in the west.

108
00:06:12,070 --> 00:06:13,000
I'm tired.

109
00:06:13,270 --> 00:06:15,130
Let's rest at the pavilion ahead.

110
00:06:26,920 --> 00:06:27,720
Attendant,

111
00:06:28,310 --> 00:06:29,190
come here.

112
00:06:44,950 --> 00:06:45,750
Your Majesty,

113
00:06:45,920 --> 00:06:47,120
what are your orders?

114
00:06:47,390 --> 00:06:48,560
It's cold.

115
00:06:48,920 --> 00:06:50,720
Go get me a blanket.

116
00:06:51,360 --> 00:06:51,920
Yes.

117
00:06:53,040 --> 00:06:53,600
Wait.

118
00:06:54,190 --> 00:06:55,190
Step forward.

119
00:06:59,600 --> 00:07:00,600
Hold your horses.

120
00:07:00,830 --> 00:07:01,510
Tonight, we will rest

121
00:07:01,510 --> 00:07:04,120
at the official post station
at Tianshui Ferry.

122
00:07:04,120 --> 00:07:05,470
We'll travel at night.

123
00:07:06,200 --> 00:07:08,230
So we can arrive
the night before Great Yong

124
00:07:08,230 --> 00:07:10,430
and Great Yan exchange their prisoners.

125
00:07:10,430 --> 00:07:11,040
Yes.

126
00:07:11,560 --> 00:07:13,600
Your Majesty, do you have anything else?

127
00:07:13,600 --> 00:07:14,630
If not,

128
00:07:14,870 --> 00:07:16,190
I will take my leave.

129
00:07:24,990 --> 00:07:25,670
My Lord.

130
00:07:26,120 --> 00:07:29,600
Keep an eye on
King Ximeng's personal guards.

131
00:07:30,240 --> 00:07:32,040
See if you can

132
00:07:32,680 --> 00:07:34,080
find any clues from them.

133
00:07:35,070 --> 00:07:35,600
Yes.

134
00:07:50,430 --> 00:07:51,830
Welcome, Your Highness.

135
00:08:13,630 --> 00:08:14,190
Come on.

136
00:08:15,120 --> 00:08:16,270
Delicious, delicious.

137
00:08:16,270 --> 00:08:17,600
This is also delicious.

138
00:08:18,270 --> 00:08:18,870
I need more.

139
00:08:18,870 --> 00:08:19,800
Come on, come on.

140
00:08:20,760 --> 00:08:22,020
Eat some meat. Come on.

141
00:08:24,190 --> 00:08:25,160
Come on. Eat some meat.

142
00:08:25,160 --> 00:08:25,720
Eat some meat.

143
00:08:25,720 --> 00:08:27,120
The meat is so delicious.

144
00:08:28,210 --> 00:08:29,540
Delicious, delicious.

145
00:08:30,040 --> 00:08:31,370
This meat is delicious.

146
00:08:32,929 --> 00:08:34,270
Meat is much better.

147
00:08:35,270 --> 00:08:36,720
Come on, eat.

148
00:08:36,750 --> 00:08:37,669
Come on, come on.

149
00:08:37,669 --> 00:08:39,070
-Eat the meat.
-Eat, eat.

150
00:08:42,549 --> 00:08:43,549
Where's the wine?

151
00:08:44,030 --> 00:08:44,910
Why do we get to eat

152
00:08:44,910 --> 00:08:46,440
dry rations and cabbage,

153
00:08:47,000 --> 00:08:48,550
while they get to eat a sumptuous meal

154
00:08:48,550 --> 00:08:49,550
with delicacies?

155
00:08:52,600 --> 00:08:54,200
Why do we get to eat this?

156
00:08:54,950 --> 00:08:56,030
We want meat!

157
00:08:56,240 --> 00:08:57,200
-Yeah!
-Yeah!

158
00:08:57,200 --> 00:08:58,360
-We want meat!
-We want meat!

159
00:08:58,360 --> 00:08:59,870
Come on, eat the meat!

160
00:09:01,750 --> 00:09:02,630
Come on, drink!

161
00:09:02,800 --> 00:09:03,680
Sirs,

162
00:09:03,710 --> 00:09:05,790
I'm really sorry for the poor service.

163
00:09:05,790 --> 00:09:07,150
You may not know this,

164
00:09:07,150 --> 00:09:10,630
but it has been pouring rain for days,

165
00:09:11,030 --> 00:09:13,120
and there are flash floods.

166
00:09:13,870 --> 00:09:15,750
The merchants
transporting fresh vegetables

167
00:09:15,750 --> 00:09:18,200
and meat to the post station
have been delayed.

168
00:09:18,200 --> 00:09:21,390
So right now,
there's not enough food here.

169
00:09:21,680 --> 00:09:24,000
I really can't arrange it.

170
00:09:29,390 --> 00:09:30,910
-Sir, Sir!
-You think we can be fooled?

171
00:09:30,910 --> 00:09:32,150
Not enough food?

172
00:09:32,960 --> 00:09:35,020
Why do they get to eat a sumptuous meal

173
00:09:35,270 --> 00:09:37,080
with delicacies?

174
00:09:41,390 --> 00:09:43,080
Calm down, Sirs, please!

175
00:09:43,440 --> 00:09:45,360
Lord Zhan arranged it this way.

176
00:09:45,360 --> 00:09:47,670
I'm just following orders.

177
00:09:47,670 --> 00:09:49,790
Please be understanding.

178
00:09:49,960 --> 00:09:52,360
A sumptuous meal!

179
00:09:53,240 --> 00:09:54,700
-Delicious!
-Delicious!

180
00:09:55,120 --> 00:09:57,480
-With delicacies!
-With delicacies!

181
00:09:57,480 --> 00:09:58,840
-Fresh!
-Fresh!

182
00:09:59,360 --> 00:10:00,610
Sirs, you can't!

183
00:10:00,630 --> 00:10:01,750
You can't!

184
00:10:01,750 --> 00:10:02,200
Sirs!

185
00:10:02,200 --> 00:10:02,910
Come on!

186
00:10:04,200 --> 00:10:07,510
A sumptuous meal is bad for your health.

187
00:10:08,310 --> 00:10:09,040
Yeah, yeah.

188
00:10:09,550 --> 00:10:13,000
Simple fare is good
for your health instead.

189
00:10:13,510 --> 00:10:14,350
Yeah, yeah.

190
00:10:14,790 --> 00:10:15,770
Let's go, come on.

191
00:10:15,770 --> 00:10:16,700
Come on, come on.

192
00:10:20,840 --> 00:10:22,510
Simple fare,

193
00:10:22,840 --> 00:10:24,390
-good health.
-good health.

194
00:10:24,390 --> 00:10:25,570
A sumptuous meal,

195
00:10:26,240 --> 00:10:28,240
-choke to death!
-choke to death!

196
00:10:28,440 --> 00:10:29,000
Eat.

197
00:10:29,440 --> 00:10:30,510
Eat. Let's eat ours.

198
00:10:30,510 --> 00:10:31,840
Come on, let's eat ours.

199
00:10:35,550 --> 00:10:36,390
What are you waiting for?

200
00:10:36,390 --> 00:10:37,320
Eat and drink.

201
00:10:54,050 --> 00:10:54,770
Let me see.

202
00:10:55,690 --> 00:10:56,330
Nothing.

203
00:10:58,600 --> 00:10:59,800
What is all this junk?

204
00:11:03,200 --> 00:11:04,120
What did you do?

205
00:11:06,720 --> 00:11:08,600
Why did you go through our bags?

206
00:11:09,170 --> 00:11:12,170
Which eye saw us going through them?

207
00:11:12,200 --> 00:11:14,000
Yeah, which eye?

208
00:11:15,200 --> 00:11:16,440
You Ximeng people

209
00:11:16,710 --> 00:11:18,390
are just like these beasts of burden,

210
00:11:18,390 --> 00:11:19,450
poor and backward.

211
00:11:19,550 --> 00:11:20,270
Tell me,

212
00:11:20,440 --> 00:11:22,030
with your ragged bags,

213
00:11:22,240 --> 00:11:23,770
what's there to go through?

214
00:11:26,500 --> 00:11:27,630
Useless fool!

215
00:11:48,960 --> 00:11:50,030
So it...

216
00:11:50,510 --> 00:11:52,510
-is a little girl!
-is a little girl!

217
00:11:54,270 --> 00:11:55,000
How dare you!

218
00:11:55,390 --> 00:11:56,450
What are you doing?

219
00:12:02,270 --> 00:12:03,200
What's going on?

220
00:12:03,390 --> 00:12:04,680
Lord Zhan, it is a—

221
00:12:04,790 --> 00:12:06,010
Lord Zhan, it is—

222
00:12:09,240 --> 00:12:10,640
Lord Zhan, it is a little—

223
00:12:23,080 --> 00:12:24,030
Lord Zhan.

224
00:12:24,910 --> 00:12:26,720
You received Her Majesty's decree

225
00:12:26,720 --> 00:12:28,720
to serve as the Guide Envoy for Ximeng,

226
00:12:28,720 --> 00:12:30,830
yet you mistreated
Ximeng's soldiers like this,

227
00:12:30,830 --> 00:12:33,270
damaging the relation
between Biantang and Ximeng.

228
00:12:33,270 --> 00:12:34,340
Acting like this,

229
00:12:34,440 --> 00:12:36,840
aren't you afraid
my mother will blame you?

230
00:12:37,200 --> 00:12:39,910
Seems you're in a bad mood today,
Your Highness.

231
00:12:40,670 --> 00:12:42,000
You reminded me

232
00:12:42,000 --> 00:12:44,080
that damaging the relation
between Ximeng and Biantang

233
00:12:44,080 --> 00:12:45,940
might incur Her Majesty's wrath.

234
00:12:46,420 --> 00:12:47,970
But I feel that

235
00:12:48,840 --> 00:12:50,550
you indiscriminately

236
00:12:50,550 --> 00:12:52,320
killed Biantang's soldiers,

237
00:12:52,670 --> 00:12:54,930
and it will enrage Her Majesty even more.

238
00:12:55,340 --> 00:12:56,850
Your Highness, do not forget one thing.

239
00:12:56,850 --> 00:12:58,780
The reason Her Majesty sent me here

240
00:12:58,790 --> 00:13:00,150
is to prevent the Crown Prince

241
00:13:00,150 --> 00:13:04,270
from doing absurd things
that disgrace Biantang.

242
00:13:04,910 --> 00:13:05,740
Lord Zhan.

243
00:13:12,120 --> 00:13:13,550
I only killed

244
00:13:13,550 --> 00:13:15,120
2 troublemaking soldiers.

245
00:13:16,120 --> 00:13:19,550
I didn't kill the Ceremonial Officer
and Guide Envoy, Lord Zhan.

246
00:13:19,550 --> 00:13:21,480
How would that disgrace Biantang?

247
00:13:27,790 --> 00:13:28,510
Why?

248
00:13:29,670 --> 00:13:31,250
Lord Zhan, are you afraid?

249
00:13:31,460 --> 00:13:33,070
It seems you remember

250
00:13:33,480 --> 00:13:35,610
that I am the Crown Prince of Biantang.

251
00:13:35,980 --> 00:13:36,730
And you,

252
00:13:37,630 --> 00:13:39,690
a Ceremonial Officer or Guide Envoy,

253
00:13:40,510 --> 00:13:41,510
in the end,

254
00:13:42,750 --> 00:13:44,550
are nothing but... but...

255
00:13:47,390 --> 00:13:48,700
a male favorite.

256
00:13:51,240 --> 00:13:52,100
Your Highness,

257
00:13:53,180 --> 00:13:54,820
whether I am a Guide Envoy

258
00:13:55,240 --> 00:13:56,550
or a male favorite,

259
00:13:56,910 --> 00:13:58,630
it's bestowed by Her Majesty.

260
00:13:59,030 --> 00:14:00,080
It's not your place to judge.

261
00:14:00,080 --> 00:14:01,670
But these troublemaking Biantang soldiers

262
00:14:01,670 --> 00:14:04,070
have already been killed
by your own hands.

263
00:14:06,200 --> 00:14:07,360
That Ximeng soldier

264
00:14:07,360 --> 00:14:10,200
should also be taken away and interrogated

265
00:14:11,800 --> 00:14:14,640
to find out what exactly is going on.

266
00:14:14,910 --> 00:14:15,550
Guards,

267
00:14:16,200 --> 00:14:17,600
arrest

268
00:14:17,600 --> 00:14:18,750
this troublemaking Ximeng soldier.

269
00:14:18,750 --> 00:14:19,410
-Yes.
-Yes.

270
00:14:22,150 --> 00:14:23,000
Hold on.

271
00:14:30,390 --> 00:14:31,320
Lord Zhan.

272
00:14:31,790 --> 00:14:33,790
Since the soldier under my command

273
00:14:33,810 --> 00:14:35,630
does not know Biantang's etiquette,

274
00:14:35,630 --> 00:14:37,750
just let me handle it.

275
00:14:38,750 --> 00:14:40,790
Take this troublemaker away

276
00:14:40,910 --> 00:14:42,550
and deal with him by military law.

277
00:14:42,550 --> 00:14:43,210
-Yes.
-Yes.

278
00:14:47,400 --> 00:14:48,080
Let go!

279
00:14:50,030 --> 00:14:50,630
Let go!

280
00:14:50,630 --> 00:14:51,510
Lord Zhan,

281
00:14:51,670 --> 00:14:53,200
am I not allowed

282
00:14:53,390 --> 00:14:55,080
to deal with my own soldier?

283
00:14:58,190 --> 00:14:58,910
Let go!

284
00:15:00,110 --> 00:15:00,780
Alright!

285
00:15:05,490 --> 00:15:06,090
Go.

286
00:15:06,340 --> 00:15:07,360
You just wait!

287
00:15:17,550 --> 00:15:18,550
The imperial map.

288
00:15:23,390 --> 00:15:24,450
The imperial pass.

289
00:15:31,200 --> 00:15:32,670
Traveling from Tangjing,

290
00:15:32,700 --> 00:15:34,360
we've already delayed
for a day on the road.

291
00:15:34,360 --> 00:15:35,960
Qingluan Pass is just ahead.

292
00:15:36,000 --> 00:15:36,960
You leave tonight.

293
00:15:36,960 --> 00:15:39,090
If you ride fast, you can still make it.

294
00:15:39,120 --> 00:15:40,720
Lincheng is an important pass
at the border

295
00:15:40,720 --> 00:15:41,790
of Great Yong and Great Yan

296
00:15:41,790 --> 00:15:43,910
and also an important military point
defended by Great Yong.

297
00:15:43,910 --> 00:15:44,720
The prisoner of war camp here

298
00:15:44,720 --> 00:15:46,840
holds important prisoners all year round.

299
00:15:46,840 --> 00:15:48,910
It might not be that easy
for you guys to succeed.

300
00:15:48,910 --> 00:15:49,910
Be very careful.

301
00:15:50,320 --> 00:15:51,000
I know.

302
00:15:53,630 --> 00:15:54,270
And,

303
00:15:55,240 --> 00:15:57,790
you don't have to return
the same way after rescuing He Xiao.

304
00:15:57,790 --> 00:16:00,030
You can circle back
to Biantang from the west.

305
00:16:00,030 --> 00:16:01,360
It'll be safer this way.

306
00:16:01,510 --> 00:16:02,480
According to the schedule,

307
00:16:02,480 --> 00:16:03,790
you should be able to arrive

308
00:16:03,790 --> 00:16:05,270
outside Tangjing in 15 days.

309
00:16:05,270 --> 00:16:07,670
Li Ce will arrange someone
to meet you then.

310
00:16:07,910 --> 00:16:08,630
Li Ce.

311
00:16:09,520 --> 00:16:11,510
You killed the guards sent by the Empress.

312
00:16:11,510 --> 00:16:13,750
You've already fallen out with Zhan Ziyu.

313
00:16:13,750 --> 00:16:15,200
He will definitely

314
00:16:15,200 --> 00:16:16,990
watch your every move in the future.

315
00:16:16,990 --> 00:16:19,520
It might be trouble
if you return to Biantang.

316
00:16:19,840 --> 00:16:20,790
My mother and I

317
00:16:21,150 --> 00:16:22,670
have actually known what kind of person

318
00:16:22,670 --> 00:16:24,150
each other is.

319
00:16:24,600 --> 00:16:26,960
We've just put on a fake show

320
00:16:26,960 --> 00:16:28,440
for over 10 years.

321
00:16:28,910 --> 00:16:30,030
She's prepared.

322
00:16:30,310 --> 00:16:31,070
So am I.

323
00:16:32,470 --> 00:16:33,120
Qiao,

324
00:16:33,950 --> 00:16:34,830
don't worry.

325
00:16:42,950 --> 00:16:45,160
[Ninghui Hall]

326
00:16:54,870 --> 00:16:56,240
Please inform His Majesty

327
00:16:56,240 --> 00:16:59,380
that Prince of Luo, Li Yan, and his future
Princess Consort, Zhao Chun'er,

328
00:16:59,380 --> 00:17:00,440
are here to seek an audience.

329
00:17:00,440 --> 00:17:01,640
His Majesty is asleep

330
00:17:01,790 --> 00:17:03,080
and hasn't left the bedchamber yet.

331
00:17:03,080 --> 00:17:04,740
It's inconvenient to report.

332
00:17:04,960 --> 00:17:06,440
It doesn't matter who you bring.

333
00:17:06,440 --> 00:17:07,700
You two just wait here.

334
00:17:22,720 --> 00:17:24,170
It's about to rain.

335
00:17:24,790 --> 00:17:26,650
How much longer do we have to wait?

336
00:17:28,349 --> 00:17:29,640
It shouldn't be too long.

337
00:17:29,640 --> 00:17:30,640
It's almost noon.

338
00:17:30,680 --> 00:17:32,480
His Majesty should wake up soon.

339
00:17:37,440 --> 00:17:38,240
Your Majesty,

340
00:17:38,920 --> 00:17:41,550
the Prince of Luo has brought his future
Princess Consort for an audience.

341
00:17:41,550 --> 00:17:42,840
They've been waiting outside the hall

342
00:17:42,840 --> 00:17:43,990
for a long time.

343
00:17:47,510 --> 00:17:48,400
Prince of Luo?

344
00:17:48,680 --> 00:17:51,140
When did I ever summon
his Princess Consort?

345
00:17:51,220 --> 00:17:51,830
Go.

346
00:17:52,350 --> 00:17:53,920
Go summon Beauty Han.

347
00:17:54,930 --> 00:17:55,520
Yes.

348
00:18:00,300 --> 00:18:01,060
Beauty Han,

349
00:18:01,080 --> 00:18:02,280
you are finally here.

350
00:18:02,400 --> 00:18:03,980
His Majesty has been talking about you
for the past two days.

351
00:18:03,980 --> 00:18:05,220
He missed you so much.

352
00:18:05,250 --> 00:18:06,460
His Majesty has been waiting
for you for a long time.

353
00:18:06,460 --> 00:18:07,720
Let's go into the hall.

354
00:18:24,360 --> 00:18:24,950
Chun'er,

355
00:18:25,490 --> 00:18:27,490
let's go wait out of the way for a bit.

356
00:18:30,510 --> 00:18:31,310
Wait!

357
00:18:36,720 --> 00:18:37,920
Where are you going?

358
00:18:38,160 --> 00:18:40,440
Didn't His Majesty tell you to wait here?

359
00:18:40,600 --> 00:18:42,190
Here means here.

360
00:18:42,640 --> 00:18:43,880
If you move,

361
00:18:44,350 --> 00:18:45,960
how can you call it here?

362
00:18:46,640 --> 00:18:47,510
Chief Fang,

363
00:18:48,310 --> 00:18:50,480
why must you make things difficult for us?

364
00:18:50,480 --> 00:18:52,350
Prince of Luo, what are you saying?

365
00:18:52,350 --> 00:18:53,440
I am but a servant.

366
00:18:53,640 --> 00:18:54,570
How would I dare?

367
00:18:57,300 --> 00:18:57,980
A vole!

368
00:18:58,000 --> 00:18:58,760
A vole!

369
00:18:59,330 --> 00:19:00,000
A vole!

370
00:19:00,030 --> 00:19:01,110
Quick! Catch it!

371
00:19:01,110 --> 00:19:02,720
Beauty Han is terrified of voles!

372
00:19:02,720 --> 00:19:03,270
Hurry!

373
00:19:04,930 --> 00:19:05,590
Where? I...

374
00:19:09,950 --> 00:19:10,560
Let's go.

375
00:19:13,460 --> 00:19:14,950
Chief Fang, are you okay?

376
00:19:28,360 --> 00:19:31,820
[Linrui Palace]

377
00:19:39,750 --> 00:19:40,440
Chun'er,

378
00:19:40,960 --> 00:19:42,360
why did you bring me here?

379
00:19:42,590 --> 00:19:44,240
Isn't this Her Majesty's bedchamber?

380
00:19:44,240 --> 00:19:45,720
We are not seeing His Majesty.

381
00:19:45,720 --> 00:19:47,350
We are going to see Her Majesty.

382
00:19:47,350 --> 00:19:49,420
Her Majesty is even less likely to see me.

383
00:19:49,420 --> 00:19:50,340
I have a plan.

384
00:20:02,070 --> 00:20:03,270
Please announce me.

385
00:20:03,880 --> 00:20:05,850
I'm the Princess Consort of Luo,
bestowed by Her Majesty.

386
00:20:05,850 --> 00:20:08,450
I have urgent matters
and must see Her Majesty.

387
00:20:12,110 --> 00:20:13,750
The Prince of Luo is not married yet.

388
00:20:13,750 --> 00:20:15,750
There is no Princess Consort of Luo.

389
00:20:17,300 --> 00:20:19,030
Give this to Her Majesty.

390
00:20:19,250 --> 00:20:20,290
She will see me.

391
00:20:30,440 --> 00:20:32,830
She says
she is the Princess Consort of Luo?

392
00:20:32,830 --> 00:20:33,550
Yes.

393
00:20:33,880 --> 00:20:35,610
She came with the Prince of Luo.

394
00:20:35,680 --> 00:20:37,140
They are waiting outside.

395
00:20:37,440 --> 00:20:38,770
Then tell her to come in.

396
00:20:39,000 --> 00:20:40,110
Just her.

397
00:20:40,720 --> 00:20:41,370
Yes.

398
00:20:46,640 --> 00:20:47,920
This jade pendant

399
00:20:47,920 --> 00:20:50,720
was a gift from Biantang

400
00:20:51,030 --> 00:20:53,680
when Noble Consort Wei
of Great Yong was pregnant.

401
00:20:53,680 --> 00:20:56,350
This is carved from Tianshan ice jade.

402
00:20:57,160 --> 00:20:58,620
It is extremely precious.

403
00:20:59,160 --> 00:21:01,070
I picked it myself.

404
00:21:01,440 --> 00:21:03,070
Since you have this jade,

405
00:21:03,240 --> 00:21:04,350
you must be...

406
00:21:06,320 --> 00:21:08,440
her executed daughter, right?

407
00:21:08,720 --> 00:21:10,920
Your Majesty, you're indeed very wise.

408
00:21:11,400 --> 00:21:12,460
My surname is Zhao,

409
00:21:12,590 --> 00:21:13,990
and my first name is Chun.

410
00:21:14,140 --> 00:21:16,040
I'm the daughter
of Noble Consort Wei of Great Yong.

411
00:21:16,040 --> 00:21:17,130
Zhao Chun'er.

412
00:21:18,110 --> 00:21:20,920
You said you are
my granted Princess Consort of Luo.

413
00:21:20,920 --> 00:21:21,990
What do you mean?

414
00:21:24,070 --> 00:21:25,930
Please forgive me, Your Majesty.

415
00:21:26,240 --> 00:21:27,960
I took precautions for you

416
00:21:28,030 --> 00:21:29,230
and took the liberty.

417
00:21:29,680 --> 00:21:31,590
Please grant my wish, Your Majesty,

418
00:21:31,590 --> 00:21:33,550
and arrange a marriage
for the Prince of Luo and me.

419
00:21:33,550 --> 00:21:36,030
Although the Prince of Luo
has no power or influence,

420
00:21:36,030 --> 00:21:38,760
he's still a member
of the Biantang royal family.

421
00:21:39,110 --> 00:21:41,070
You are just a deposed princess,

422
00:21:41,300 --> 00:21:42,900
who is still guilty.

423
00:21:43,590 --> 00:21:44,960
Why do you think

424
00:21:45,440 --> 00:21:47,840
I would allow you
to marry the Prince of Luo?

425
00:21:47,880 --> 00:21:49,010
Because this matter

426
00:21:49,430 --> 00:21:50,860
is a win-win situation

427
00:21:51,310 --> 00:21:52,480
for both of us.

428
00:22:00,410 --> 00:22:02,170
I'd like to hear it.

429
00:22:03,270 --> 00:22:04,330
Stand up and speak.

430
00:22:10,440 --> 00:22:12,570
Three years ago, I offended my father,

431
00:22:12,930 --> 00:22:14,850
but now he is old and sick.

432
00:22:15,080 --> 00:22:16,830
Today in Great Yong, my brother,

433
00:22:16,830 --> 00:22:19,400
the Prince of Xiang, Zhao Che,
is in charge of the state.

434
00:22:19,400 --> 00:22:20,730
He holds military power

435
00:22:20,890 --> 00:22:22,400
and has the support of the people.

436
00:22:22,400 --> 00:22:24,600
He'll surely be Great Yong's next king.

437
00:22:25,240 --> 00:22:26,500
Although I am deposed,

438
00:22:26,830 --> 00:22:28,070
my brother Zhao Che

439
00:22:28,140 --> 00:22:29,670
has always loved me dearly.

440
00:22:30,500 --> 00:22:31,880
Before I came to Biantang,

441
00:22:31,880 --> 00:22:33,400
I had been living in the army.

442
00:22:33,400 --> 00:22:36,000
If you're willing to ignore my past

443
00:22:36,310 --> 00:22:38,310
and arrange a marriage
for the Prince of Luo and me,

444
00:22:38,310 --> 00:22:40,350
I can write to my brother.

445
00:22:41,250 --> 00:22:42,830
I will use this marriage as an excuse

446
00:22:42,830 --> 00:22:45,430
to beg him to restore
my identity as a princess.

447
00:22:47,960 --> 00:22:48,830
Why do you think

448
00:22:48,830 --> 00:22:51,050
the Prince of Xiang
will agree to your request?

449
00:22:51,050 --> 00:22:52,730
Just because he dotes on you?

450
00:22:56,720 --> 00:22:58,920
Your Majesty, you hold a high position.

451
00:22:59,110 --> 00:23:00,840
You should know better than me.

452
00:23:01,110 --> 00:23:03,310
A princess married to Biantang,

453
00:23:03,640 --> 00:23:05,720
compared to a dead deposed princess,

454
00:23:06,400 --> 00:23:08,460
is more beneficial to both Great Yong

455
00:23:08,920 --> 00:23:10,250
and the Prince of Xiang.

456
00:23:11,070 --> 00:23:12,480
For you,

457
00:23:13,750 --> 00:23:15,070
it should be the same.

458
00:23:41,880 --> 00:23:42,550
How is it?

459
00:23:43,310 --> 00:23:45,480
Her Majesty has arranged
a marriage for us.

460
00:23:45,480 --> 00:23:46,550
Really, Chun'er?

461
00:23:46,680 --> 00:23:48,940
It's scheduled for the 5th of next month.

462
00:23:49,270 --> 00:23:50,000
Great!

463
00:23:50,400 --> 00:23:51,400
Great, Chun'er!

464
00:24:08,480 --> 00:24:09,110
Princess,

465
00:24:09,750 --> 00:24:10,400
someone has been following us

466
00:24:10,400 --> 00:24:11,720
since last night.

467
00:24:12,070 --> 00:24:13,530
He's followed us for 40 li.

468
00:24:13,830 --> 00:24:14,590
I guess

469
00:24:14,750 --> 00:24:17,110
it's a tall young man,

470
00:24:17,750 --> 00:24:20,010
and his martial arts skills aren't weak.

471
00:24:20,310 --> 00:24:21,070
Ignore him.

472
00:24:27,960 --> 00:24:28,490
Let's go.

473
00:24:29,520 --> 00:24:31,250
Take a look. They are all fresh.

474
00:24:40,480 --> 00:24:42,810
Beyond the Baichuan River lies Lincheng.

475
00:24:42,880 --> 00:24:44,140
I see an inn over there.

476
00:24:44,480 --> 00:24:45,680
Why don't we stay here

477
00:24:45,790 --> 00:24:46,880
for the night?

478
00:25:02,270 --> 00:25:05,070
Sir, you wear a blue robe.
Might your surname be Xi?

479
00:25:05,830 --> 00:25:06,790
My surname is not Xi.

480
00:25:06,790 --> 00:25:09,440
A female guest said your surname is Xi.

481
00:25:09,830 --> 00:25:12,270
The appearance and temperament
she described

482
00:25:12,270 --> 00:25:14,000
are exactly like yours.

483
00:25:14,310 --> 00:25:17,070
Only the age doesn't match.

484
00:25:17,310 --> 00:25:19,310
She said it was an old man.

485
00:25:21,830 --> 00:25:22,630
That's right.

486
00:25:22,880 --> 00:25:23,880
I am the old man.

487
00:25:26,030 --> 00:25:27,230
What else did she say?

488
00:25:27,900 --> 00:25:29,860
She has already arranged

489
00:25:29,920 --> 00:25:31,240
your room and food.

490
00:25:31,440 --> 00:25:34,200
The room is a bit small,

491
00:25:35,110 --> 00:25:37,350
but she said you're old

492
00:25:37,350 --> 00:25:38,810
and have mobility issues,

493
00:25:39,030 --> 00:25:39,830
so she specifically informed me

494
00:25:39,830 --> 00:25:42,680
to tell you to be careful on the stairs.

495
00:25:44,240 --> 00:25:45,920
But you don't seem old to me.

496
00:25:46,110 --> 00:25:47,590
Then just follow her arrangements.

497
00:25:47,590 --> 00:25:49,270
Okay, please come this way.

498
00:25:55,220 --> 00:25:56,300
Sorry, Sir.

499
00:25:56,410 --> 00:25:59,500
The food was also arranged
by the female guest.

500
00:25:59,720 --> 00:26:02,440
She said you are over 60

501
00:26:02,490 --> 00:26:03,610
and have poor teeth,

502
00:26:03,610 --> 00:26:05,470
so you should have some porridge.

503
00:26:08,830 --> 00:26:09,720
Bring me a pot of aged wine.

504
00:26:09,720 --> 00:26:10,290
Okay.

505
00:26:10,920 --> 00:26:12,550
A pot of aged wine.

506
00:26:18,860 --> 00:26:21,690
With the continuous wars
between Great Yan and Great Yong,

507
00:26:21,690 --> 00:26:23,970
the leather business is getting harder.

508
00:26:24,000 --> 00:26:24,660
That's all.

509
00:26:25,200 --> 00:26:27,680
Just the transportation costs

510
00:26:28,240 --> 00:26:29,840
have multiplied several times.

511
00:26:29,840 --> 00:26:31,370
There's no money to be made.

512
00:26:32,920 --> 00:26:34,550
With the wars every year,

513
00:26:35,160 --> 00:26:37,680
my inn's business is also sluggish.

514
00:26:38,440 --> 00:26:39,240
You know what?

515
00:26:39,790 --> 00:26:41,640
Soon, Great Yan and Great Yong

516
00:26:41,640 --> 00:26:43,190
are going to exchange prisoners of war,

517
00:26:43,190 --> 00:26:46,250
so there are actually more travelers
passing through.

518
00:26:46,790 --> 00:26:48,240
Haven't Great Yong and Great Yan

519
00:26:48,240 --> 00:26:49,640
been at war all this time?

520
00:26:49,750 --> 00:26:51,130
Why are they suddenly exchanging prisoners

521
00:26:51,130 --> 00:26:52,450
at a time like this?

522
00:26:52,920 --> 00:26:54,590
It is said that among these prisoners

523
00:26:54,590 --> 00:26:56,160
are the former Xiuli Army.

524
00:26:56,240 --> 00:26:57,510
Chu Qiao has gone missing.

525
00:26:57,510 --> 00:26:59,110
In order to lure Chu Qiao out,

526
00:26:59,240 --> 00:27:00,830
the King of Great Yan is said
to be willing to do whatever it takes

527
00:27:00,830 --> 00:27:02,490
to exchange these prisoners.

528
00:27:02,750 --> 00:27:03,720
Have you heard?

529
00:27:03,720 --> 00:27:04,790
The King of Great Yan

530
00:27:04,790 --> 00:27:07,880
is considered a young warlord
dominating the region.

531
00:27:08,310 --> 00:27:10,200
But he is deeply in love

532
00:27:10,720 --> 00:27:12,960
with the female general Chu Qiao.

533
00:27:14,000 --> 00:27:14,790
That Chu Qiao

534
00:27:14,790 --> 00:27:17,320
was killed by Great Yong's
general Zhuge Yue.

535
00:27:18,620 --> 00:27:19,970
It is said that this Chu Qiao

536
00:27:19,970 --> 00:27:21,830
was once a female slave
of the Zhuge family.

537
00:27:21,830 --> 00:27:24,320
The Zhuge family
has kept slaves for generations.

538
00:27:24,320 --> 00:27:25,790
Especially this Zhuge Yue,

539
00:27:25,790 --> 00:27:27,680
who is the heir of their family.

540
00:27:28,350 --> 00:27:30,200
Who knows how many female slaves

541
00:27:30,200 --> 00:27:31,600
have been killed by them.

542
00:27:31,980 --> 00:27:33,690
Life and death are at others' mercy.

543
00:27:33,690 --> 00:27:34,890
How pathetic.

544
00:27:35,440 --> 00:27:37,200
But God has eyes.

545
00:27:37,370 --> 00:27:39,170
He also died in this frozen lake.

546
00:27:51,030 --> 00:27:51,720
My Lord.

547
00:27:51,810 --> 00:27:53,910
We've found out
General He's exact location.

548
00:27:53,910 --> 00:27:55,930
But Lincheng is Great Yong's territory.

549
00:27:55,930 --> 00:27:57,960
I'm afraid many in the Yong Army know you.

550
00:27:57,960 --> 00:27:59,920
The Black Eagle Army
is also stationed nearby.

551
00:27:59,920 --> 00:28:01,070
Our actions

552
00:28:01,570 --> 00:28:02,720
will easily attract attention.

553
00:28:02,720 --> 00:28:07,680
[Border between Great Yong and Great Yan]
[Prisoner of War Camp, Lincheng]

554
00:28:04,920 --> 00:28:06,120
Tomorrow, Great Yong

555
00:28:06,230 --> 00:28:08,680
will exchange prisoners of war
with Great Yan.

556
00:28:08,680 --> 00:28:10,160
They definitely won't let anything happen

557
00:28:10,160 --> 00:28:11,690
to He Xiao the night before.

558
00:28:11,830 --> 00:28:14,550
Xiao Ran only needs to set a fire
in the corner of the prisoner of war camp.

559
00:28:14,550 --> 00:28:16,680
He Xiao will definitely be relocated.

560
00:28:16,880 --> 00:28:17,590
Go!

561
00:28:17,670 --> 00:28:19,270
Hurry, go get water!

562
00:28:19,290 --> 00:28:19,900
All right.

563
00:28:21,960 --> 00:28:22,550
Let's go.

564
00:28:22,830 --> 00:28:23,790
Follow them

565
00:28:24,110 --> 00:28:26,350
and see where they'll move to.

566
00:28:30,680 --> 00:28:33,030
In 4 hours, when the sky is gray,

567
00:28:33,030 --> 00:28:35,160
people's minds will be least alert.

568
00:28:35,790 --> 00:28:38,480
I will go in and rescue He Xiao then.

569
00:28:39,030 --> 00:28:39,680
Xiao Ran,

570
00:28:40,310 --> 00:28:42,440
you wait outside the city to back us up.

571
00:28:42,590 --> 00:28:43,450
Fang Miaomiao,

572
00:28:43,880 --> 00:28:45,960
go to Baichuan Ferry and find a boat.

573
00:28:46,790 --> 00:28:48,070
We'll leave by water.

574
00:28:53,440 --> 00:28:55,770
A fire broke out
in the middle of the night.

575
00:28:56,300 --> 00:28:57,980
What the hell.

576
00:29:00,960 --> 00:29:01,820
Who do you want?

577
00:29:01,960 --> 00:29:03,160
If you want to live,

578
00:29:03,440 --> 00:29:05,770
take me
to the Commander of the Xiuli Army,

579
00:29:05,830 --> 00:29:06,830
He Xiao.

580
00:29:07,030 --> 00:29:07,680
You...

581
00:29:08,510 --> 00:29:09,720
Where exactly is he?

582
00:29:09,960 --> 00:29:10,550
He's...

583
00:29:11,550 --> 00:29:12,440
He's inside.

584
00:29:12,570 --> 00:29:13,960
If you dare lie to me,

585
00:29:14,510 --> 00:29:16,070
I will kill you on the spot.

586
00:29:16,640 --> 00:29:17,200
Go.

587
00:29:19,420 --> 00:29:20,640
Damn He Xiao.

588
00:29:20,840 --> 00:29:23,160
You killed so many
of our Great Yong people

589
00:29:23,160 --> 00:29:24,890
and still want to be exchanged?

590
00:29:25,930 --> 00:29:26,790
In your dreams!

591
00:29:27,160 --> 00:29:28,820
Even for a prisoner exchange,

592
00:29:28,880 --> 00:29:30,440
I'll cripple you first.

593
00:29:30,680 --> 00:29:32,280
When you return to Great Yan,

594
00:29:32,350 --> 00:29:34,810
you'll be a cripple
for the rest of your life.

595
00:29:38,240 --> 00:29:38,960
Inside.

596
00:29:47,260 --> 00:29:48,020
Where is he?

597
00:29:48,640 --> 00:29:49,400
Inside.

598
00:29:49,590 --> 00:29:50,750
He Xiao is inside.

599
00:30:00,590 --> 00:30:01,240
He Xiao.

600
00:30:02,200 --> 00:30:02,830
He Xiao.

601
00:30:18,360 --> 00:30:19,220
General Cheng,

602
00:30:19,750 --> 00:30:21,610
thanks for your timely reminder.

603
00:30:21,750 --> 00:30:22,720
Otherwise,

604
00:30:23,550 --> 00:30:25,880
we would have lost the key prisoner today.

605
00:30:28,020 --> 00:30:29,500
Put out the fire! Put out the fire!

606
00:30:29,090 --> 00:30:30,500
[4 hours ago]

607
00:30:29,840 --> 00:30:31,880
Lock all the prisoners
in the wooden cells!

608
00:30:31,880 --> 00:30:32,510
Hurry!

609
00:30:32,790 --> 00:30:33,550
Lord Liu.

610
00:30:33,790 --> 00:30:34,310
Hurry!

611
00:30:34,330 --> 00:30:35,060
Who's there?

612
00:30:35,270 --> 00:30:37,880
I'm Cheng Yuan,
Commander of Great Yan's Black Eagle Army.

613
00:30:37,880 --> 00:30:38,480
Coming!

614
00:30:39,310 --> 00:30:40,840
The official report states

615
00:30:41,440 --> 00:30:42,960
that the Great Yan general

616
00:30:43,050 --> 00:30:45,050
escorting the prisoners is Shi Yan.

617
00:30:45,110 --> 00:30:47,680
What is your purpose here, General Cheng?

618
00:30:47,680 --> 00:30:49,920
Lord Liu, you have such great composure.

619
00:30:49,920 --> 00:30:51,580
You can barely save yourself,

620
00:30:52,110 --> 00:30:53,640
yet you still care about me.

621
00:30:56,440 --> 00:30:57,370
What do you mean?

622
00:30:57,640 --> 00:31:00,720
Do you think this fire is a coincidence?

623
00:31:01,270 --> 00:31:02,930
If you move the prisoners now,

624
00:31:03,310 --> 00:31:05,310
you will fall into the enemy's trap.

625
00:31:05,480 --> 00:31:06,200
Chu Qiao,

626
00:31:07,240 --> 00:31:08,720
you can die in peace.

627
00:31:27,680 --> 00:31:28,290
Xing.

628
00:31:28,630 --> 00:31:29,430
Zhuge Yue?

629
00:31:29,690 --> 00:31:30,890
Kill Zhuge Yue for me!

630
00:31:51,100 --> 00:31:51,690
Go.

631
00:31:52,190 --> 00:31:53,270
Assassins!

632
00:32:07,070 --> 00:32:08,750
Hurry! Keep searching!

633
00:32:10,310 --> 00:32:10,880
Hurry!

634
00:32:17,400 --> 00:32:18,200
What's wrong?

635
00:32:19,090 --> 00:32:20,390
We have to split up.

636
00:32:20,480 --> 00:32:22,030
Otherwise, it'll be too conspicuous.

637
00:32:22,030 --> 00:32:23,000
You go that way.

638
00:32:23,000 --> 00:32:25,030
I'll take the main road ahead
to distract them.

639
00:32:25,030 --> 00:32:26,630
We'll meet outside Xicheng.

640
00:32:27,270 --> 00:32:27,880
Okay.

641
00:32:33,240 --> 00:32:35,480
Fang Miaomiao and the others
are at Baichuan Ferry.

642
00:32:35,480 --> 00:32:36,720
If you can't wait for me,

643
00:32:36,720 --> 00:32:37,960
we'll meet at the ferry.

644
00:32:37,960 --> 00:32:38,550
Okay.

645
00:32:43,470 --> 00:32:44,200
Don't worry.

646
00:32:44,620 --> 00:32:45,210
Go.

647
00:33:05,070 --> 00:33:06,130
Search carefully!

648
00:33:06,200 --> 00:33:07,400
Don't miss any clues!

649
00:33:07,400 --> 00:33:08,330
Find them for me!

650
00:33:08,350 --> 00:33:09,110
-Yes!
-Yes!

651
00:33:16,350 --> 00:33:17,030
Zhuge Yue!

652
00:33:18,680 --> 00:33:19,390
Zhuge Yue!

653
00:33:23,210 --> 00:33:23,900
Zhuge Yue!

654
00:33:25,790 --> 00:33:26,790
You are poisoned?

655
00:33:28,890 --> 00:33:29,750
There's movement over there.

656
00:33:29,750 --> 00:33:30,950
Everyone, follow me.

657
00:33:32,030 --> 00:33:32,470
Go.

658
00:33:32,960 --> 00:33:33,490
Hurry up.

659
00:33:40,310 --> 00:33:41,000
They are there.

660
00:33:41,000 --> 00:33:41,660
Chase them!

661
00:33:55,860 --> 00:33:57,030
Over there! Go!

662
00:34:08,110 --> 00:34:09,239
They are over there!

663
00:34:14,360 --> 00:34:14,960
Xing,

664
00:34:15,710 --> 00:34:16,230
you...

665
00:34:17,230 --> 00:34:18,000
Zhuge Yue,

666
00:34:18,710 --> 00:34:20,370
we will live and die together.

667
00:34:23,400 --> 00:34:24,060
Over there!

668
00:34:25,409 --> 00:34:26,150
Stop!

669
00:34:38,750 --> 00:34:39,750
Such a high cliff,

670
00:34:40,320 --> 00:34:41,630
they won't survive.

671
00:34:41,650 --> 00:34:42,510
Let's retreat.

672
00:34:48,760 --> 00:34:49,840
Why are you alone?

673
00:34:49,860 --> 00:34:50,520
Where is Princess Fu?

674
00:34:50,520 --> 00:34:51,360
She didn't show up.

675
00:34:51,360 --> 00:34:52,480
There's a curfew in the city.

676
00:34:52,480 --> 00:34:53,400
The Great Yong soldiers

677
00:34:53,400 --> 00:34:54,630
and the Black Eagle Army
are both searching for her.

678
00:34:54,630 --> 00:34:55,800
Why is the Black Eagle Army here?

679
00:34:55,800 --> 00:34:56,550
I don't know either.

680
00:34:56,550 --> 00:34:58,350
We must find a way to save her now.

681
00:34:58,590 --> 00:34:59,450
General Cheng.

682
00:35:02,670 --> 00:35:04,760
Does your wound hurt?

683
00:35:05,110 --> 00:35:06,670
I'll go get a physician for you.

684
00:35:06,670 --> 00:35:08,000
No need, Lord Liu.

685
00:35:08,510 --> 00:35:09,840
It's just a flesh wound.

686
00:35:09,840 --> 00:35:10,770
It won't kill me.

687
00:35:12,110 --> 00:35:14,110
I have some imperial medicine

688
00:35:14,630 --> 00:35:16,110
from the Great Yong Palace.

689
00:35:16,110 --> 00:35:17,920
Within 3 days of application,

690
00:35:18,110 --> 00:35:20,510
the wound will heal naturally.

691
00:35:21,030 --> 00:35:22,160
It's very precious.

692
00:35:25,000 --> 00:35:26,130
Thank you, Lord Liu.

693
00:35:26,550 --> 00:35:27,480
You're welcome.

694
00:35:28,030 --> 00:35:31,400
Thanks to your great help today,

695
00:35:31,400 --> 00:35:32,960
I didn't lose the key prisoner.

696
00:35:32,960 --> 00:35:35,670
I am deeply grateful.

697
00:35:42,280 --> 00:35:43,230
It's a pity

698
00:35:44,960 --> 00:35:46,320
that they escaped.

699
00:35:47,480 --> 00:35:48,190
Lord Liu.

700
00:35:48,960 --> 00:35:50,110
If you live,

701
00:35:50,710 --> 00:35:53,110
someone will know what happened tonight.

702
00:35:53,770 --> 00:35:54,550
Then I

703
00:35:55,280 --> 00:35:56,880
won't be able to live either.

704
00:36:21,740 --> 00:36:22,530
Chu,

705
00:36:22,740 --> 00:36:24,670
the law of the jungle
prevails in this world.

706
00:36:24,670 --> 00:36:26,470
There is no justice or fairness.

707
00:36:26,740 --> 00:36:27,380
Xing,

708
00:36:27,710 --> 00:36:29,040
to the ends of the earth,

709
00:36:29,280 --> 00:36:30,680
we live and die together.

710
00:36:30,920 --> 00:36:32,230
To the new King of Great Yan!

711
00:36:32,230 --> 00:36:32,920
Cheers!

712
00:36:34,000 --> 00:36:35,850
You kept saying you liked me!

713
00:36:35,880 --> 00:36:37,070
You liar!

714
00:36:39,370 --> 00:36:40,160
Remember,

715
00:36:40,350 --> 00:36:43,280
you are not allowed
to hide anything from me anymore.

716
00:36:44,530 --> 00:36:45,480
Kill her.

